{"tid":1531813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句簡單話比你知點解人群起話唔好放火魔法","createTime":"2019-09-02T10:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T11:39:06.000Z","uid":81236,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"faa9301d861fa946df68d6601b119c4f54ab8a21","tid":1531813,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"他又說，社會上仍有默許暴力的現象，敦促市民一同向暴力說不。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為政府已經留意到社會上有默許用唔同魔法既共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以點解班官成日出黎叫人割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次都算係政府認證最怕就係唔市民唔割席<br />\n<br />\n我就死人塌樓核爆都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306f7b428ce64672b12d83e461902fc154ecc382","tid":1531813,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"氣車炸彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0e80690a7f1c4e915273a49d72638aaf0736ab","tid":1531813,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:41:55.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c712ad05f3058df1d63e30d7e6909eaab3a811","tid":1531813,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家係要諗方法拖呀，你罷工都冇人升咩級，勇武始終係少數你迫唔到和理非做勇武，但係民意唔割已經係最大後盾，根本而家政府急唔係我地急，明知佢十月一死線你就咪撚自己整死自己啦，個個星期keep住50到100萬人遊行你睇邊個死先，次撚次想即日見到效果嘅人先最唔好出嚟講革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪又唔記得咗係長期戰呀<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530256</a>"},{"pid":"a6ec60350ffeae726a9f2c03e43d274846b245e6","tid":1531813,"uid":284038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:45:05.000Z","msg":"唔係無差別攻擊就得<br />\n事實上得對家會無差別"},{"pid":"4caf57119e4b448ef8b56349f5d7f5d5f21b2219","tid":1531813,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6ec60350ffeae726a9f2c03e43d274846b245e6","tid":1531813,"uid":284038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:45:05.000Z","msg":"唔係無差別攻擊就得<br />\n事實上得對家會無差別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"所以對方點解用盡所有方法要我地割席"},{"pid":"ab84b5abe012acd1147d874a546cb3f7b971d48b","tid":1531813,"uid":245033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"火攻唔小心打中我都唔割"},{"pid":"3d55871c67a1a5c3ee9540a7c52cbaa095d3ac09","tid":1531813,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:57:54.000Z","msg":"所有掟唔中啲狗嘅魔法都要割𥱊"},{"pid":"d744e95fa35c3d5d460cb72eae17147572eff114","tid":1531813,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d55871c67a1a5c3ee9540a7c52cbaa095d3ac09","tid":1531813,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:57:54.000Z","msg":"所有掟唔中啲狗嘅魔法都要割𥱊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:03:08.000Z","msg":"要練習既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcf35bd04ef35d2632861bf1ae79005c9112bea","tid":1531813,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4229306ed89ecfb0b83a14890b271eb89911ac05","tid":1531813,"uid":287410,"like":0,"